data.name: Black Cat-astrophe
data.desc: During your opponent's Battle Phase, if you control 2 or more face-down Defense Position monsters: End the Battle Phase. You can banish this card from your Graveyard, then target 2 face-up monsters on the field, including at least 1 "Prediction Princess" monster; change them to face-down Defense Position.

card_sets.set_name: Dragons of Legend: The Complete Series
